# Design references dropped in for this build, not part of the site. Kept on
# disk, deliberately out of the repo — nothing here is imported by the build,
# and all of it is preserved in the original IDEA-INCUBATOR-ECELL repo.
#
# idea-heropage-v1 / ideaclublogoeffect carry their own .git (they would land
# as broken embedded repos); ideaclublogoeffect also carries node_modules plus
# the 31MB ungraded source clip. The graded frames we ship live in
# public/sequence. winners/ is the saved Next.js build the cube scene was read
# out of; about.2/ is a separate mini-project.
/idea-heropage-v1/
/ideaclublogoeffect/
/winners/
/about.2/

# Faculty portraits duplicated at the repo root; the site loads them from
# public/faculty/, which is what MENTORS[].photo points at.
